1. 
StackOverflowError happen because the value n will keep decreasing and will never
satisfy the base case.

2.
StackOverflowError happen when value n entered is equal or greater than 1 because
the value n will keep increasing and never satisfy the base case.

3.
public String reverse(String word) {
    int i = word.length;
    String reversed = "";
    if (word.length == 1) {
        reversed += word[i];
    }
    reversed += word[i];

    return reversed;
}


4.
public int addition(int n) {
    int total = 0;
    if (n == 1) {
        return 1;
    }
    n = n + addition(n-1);
}